# setSearchTokenResult(_:)

**Instance Method**

Sets a paste item’s search token from an item provider.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor func setSearchTokenResult(_ token: UISearchToken)
```

## Parameters

- **token**: The token for the item to paste.
